# PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0

This license applies to **everything in this repository**: the Rust
workspace under `crates/`, the `examples/`, `docs/`, `installer/`, and
`scripts/` trees, the workspace manifests (`Cargo.toml`, `deny.toml`,
`rust-toolchain.toml`, `Justfile`, `dist-workspace.toml`), the docs
(`README.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`, `THREATS.md`, `PROJECT_BRIEF.md`,
`USE_CASES.md`, `use-cases/`), the `.github/` workflows, and any other
project-owned file in this tree. The bundled `yt-dlp` binary retains its
upstream **Unlicense** terms (shipped at the per-OS bundled-binary install
path as `yt-dlp-LICENSE.txt`); the bundled `ffmpeg` binary retains its
**LGPL-2.1+** terms (shipped similarly as `ffmpeg-LICENSE.txt`).

