## Bundled fonts

This project bundles font files inside the binary to give users a
deterministic look across operating systems. The bundled fonts and their
copyrights:

- **Inter** (Regular / Medium / SemiBold / Bold) — Copyright 2020 The Inter
  Project Authors, <https://github.com/rsms/inter>.
- **JetBrains Mono** (Regular) — Copyright 2020 The JetBrains Mono Project
  Authors, <https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono>.

Both fonts are licensed under the **SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1**.
The full text of that license is reproduced below, and a copy ships in the
source tree at `crates/app/assets/fonts/LICENSE.OFL.txt`. The OFL applies
only to the font files in `crates/app/assets/fonts/*.ttf`; the rest of this
repository remains governed by the PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0 license
above.

